{"tid":1080812,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想用左三文魚代替海帶黎煲綠豆沙 值得一試","createTime":"2019-03-28T00:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T04:25:19.000Z","uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"00c90ca77d4aa2d7405e1451895cbbbf5b6bbcae","tid":1080812,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"我老豆做酒樓部長<br />\n<br />\n尋日食飯聽佢講傳統酒樓d紅豆沙咁香係因為除左陳皮之外仲有落豬油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就諗 平時d綠豆沙無果種咁既香味唔通係因為無落油<br />\n綠豆沙仲要落左海帶呢d口感勁差既垃圾<br />\n<br />\n於是為左取代原來海帶果種海水味 仲要有油脂既香味我用左一細舊三文魚(樓下citysuper買既 冰鮮約40蚊 我切左半舊放落去)<br />\n<br />\n三文魚仲要有好天然既蛋白質既香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落細細舊亦都唔會搶到綠豆沙味<br />\n<br />\n為左有少少海帶果種清清地既味 我落左少少薄荷 一兩塊葉 都係吊下味<br />\n<br />\n煮果時都係同煲綠豆沙差唔多做法 youtube好多片 海帶果個位換做三文魚就ok<br />\n個人鍾意甜 落左兩舊片糖 <br />\n<br />\n舊三文魚甜甜地其實都唔錯"},{"pid":"e20e126591087baa6ae1262b30b8a5a0f960a427","tid":1080812,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:46:58.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"09f2c30bf79483011c3fce3ac8b7bbddbb0ff5e5","tid":1080812,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"1b9bbd394849e02b79c063071bb870c3e65e1395","tid":1080812,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e20e126591087baa6ae1262b30b8a5a0f960a427","tid":1080812,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:46:58.000Z","msg":"圖?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:47:40.000Z","msg":"綠豆沙一兜 外型無分別"},{"pid":"016ceefba0fcbc8544a79f877e49d7083c514d17","tid":1080812,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:49:52.000Z","msg":"無圖就咪開post<br />\n起碼都要有張撈到三文魚嘅綠豆沙圖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf401d9174d69cd5485f6d3cc5ead7ba8b6bdbc0","tid":1080812,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy